Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:41.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(500,500)}本字幕由豌豆字幕組&風之聖殿字幕組聯合製作 \N僅供學習交流 禁止用於商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:10.03,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:23.54,oped,,0,0,0,,初出茅廬的我 面對充滿未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:35.30,oped,,0,0,0,,像那一天一色的晨空般 無數次驚訝不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:45.98,oped,,0,0,0,,現在正鐫刻歷史 胸中也滿溢思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:51.57,oped,,0,0,0,,定能創造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:58.16,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:03.79,oped,,0,0,0,,一切都光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:09.29,oped,,0,0,0,,不為人知的自己 發現未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:24.56,oped,,0,0,0,,我不懈追尋 那最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.23,oped,,0,0,0,,永不停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.59,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,發生奇蹟的機率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.57,oped,,0,0,0,,根本無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.07,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.16,oped,,0,0,0,,或許只是神明的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.30,oped,,0,0,0,,明天的天空會是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:32.09,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們去看看 那未知的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:39.27,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:44.65,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.40,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:55.99,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情…或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.54,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,262)}那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.67,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這不是能感覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是因為我的眼力很強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 當然是我的眼力更強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼 有什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好好看啊 我釋放出了超強的眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.40,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和神社和動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小丫頭能做成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你還吃那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再吃一碗也沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雞肉糰子也好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是爸爸教我做的 下次在中式粥裡也放一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小丫頭的菜譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}吃完了就快點準備出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都會來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你要乖乖躲在包裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}別說夢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們繼續昨晚的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我要棉花糖和蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}媽媽要吃小蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這就是日本的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你是第一次見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以前在照片上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道觀月老師怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是我們小學時的班導師 現在在英國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}觀月老師是這個神社的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說到神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}髮型好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是莓鈴幫我卷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有卷髮器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她就幫我編麻花辮 用濕巾弄出了這種效果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然沒有定型噴霧 不過維持今天一天還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總感覺 最近我說話經常被打斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}被一種強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望這強大的力量一直都發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學會晚一點到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他說到了神社會聯繫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼居然會遲到 真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他一般都會提前十分鐘到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他應該是有什麼事吧 我們先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也對 畢竟今天的主角是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你真是毫不動搖啊 小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}日本神社裡的集市原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽說你沒在有集市的時候來過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且秋穗也沒見過神社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家當時也在動物園和神社中糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後山崎同學查了集市的日子 發現剛好是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺國內國外的動物園可能沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說到神社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抽神籤也很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抽神籤？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是占卜用的竹籤 結果會寫在紙上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 也好想一起去一次動物園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有機會請務必一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}動物園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:06:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}昨天那是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴是貓 其他人會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 動物園裡沒有貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的有好多商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以前是賣古玩的居多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}最近也有賣點心和餐具的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有各式各樣的形狀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個是不是很像小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 每一個都是100日元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}當作紀念品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會珍藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還是吃了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個好好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想用它來放醃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}奈緒子現在還在用糠床做醃菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}糠床？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道 有很多酵素對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}會是什麼味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}糠床是不能吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要在糠床裡醃各種菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}最適合用來做醃菜的是直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}NASA每年都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}直升機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你的事情忙完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你去了那個烤薄餅店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 超鬆軟超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個咖啡牛奶好好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 我還買了豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是給海渡的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們兩個一起來日本的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不要這麼緊張 我又不會搶你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 會被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有人幫助我 所以還好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個 李同學你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}叫我莓鈴就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那莓鈴 你來日本的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也有照顧我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}習慣這邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然還有很多不懂的地方 不過大家都很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 確實都是老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 他們自己是不知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然是物以類聚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不要揉眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你怎麼了 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們喝完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大 大家的耳朵 耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}耳朵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是在小攤上買的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有小攤賣動物的耳朵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}尾巴？ 你們連尾巴也買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了 木之本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你在說什麼喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了咩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}蹦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有什麼奇怪的嗎汪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}汪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都長出了動物的耳朵和尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}耳朵和尾巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼回事 大家去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是哪裡啊 什麼時候到了這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我發現大家都長出了動物的耳朵 然後突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在不是開玩笑的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看到了不合常理的畫面 不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是這到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總之 這肯定是那個搞的鬼 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}隱藏著夢之力量的鑰匙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在我面前顯示你真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼會變成動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有這裡到底是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我覺得這都是新卡牌搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你能感覺到氣息是從哪裡發出的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感 感覺四周全都有氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}全都有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是哪裡的一點 而是周圍都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那要怎麼把它變成卡牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你的朋友們也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 為什麼大家會變成動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是但是 還是有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總覺得大家比剛剛更像動物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}基本就是動物了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}得趕緊想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼辦啊 要是大家就這麼變不回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我用魔法停止了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我的魔力不能維持太久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}趕緊找出原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我不知道 周圍全都有氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說是動物的耳朵對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼都行 就算是很細微的事情也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天在糾結是去神社還是去動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就在想 也挺想去動物園的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後等我注意到的時候 周圍就變成草原了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都變得像動物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還在漸漸變成真正的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還是害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能深呼吸一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我的魔法很快就會解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你要想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想要變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想要大家變回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想和大家回到原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就去強烈地渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓大家變回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和大家回到原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小狼一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼 小可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}嚇死我了 突然就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我讓他們帶我去神社後面看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.41,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.10,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他在森林裡轉暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學 還要喝點水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以李同學才不舒服的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為強行使用了讓時間停止的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我只是在變回原樣的時候失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好遜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以你就不要擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我聽阿姨他們說你進行了艱苦的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過看來還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這些都是為了木之本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我現在很不甘心 為什麼我沒有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}即使沒有魔力 你也幫了我和小櫻很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你叫她「小櫻」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好啦好啦 血壓別升高了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不然又會不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說起來 你對木之本的髮型發表感想了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「幻影」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「MIRAGE」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這張卡牌把我所想的事變成現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為我很害怕 所以變成了更可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是小狼阻止了事情惡化 他肯定勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}停止時間可是高級魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖說他是李家人 知道很多咒語和術式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但實際用起來還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很艱難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也不知道新卡牌以後還會引發什麼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在那種時候 為了不讓大家難過和害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家該休息的時候都休息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡是有福不用忙的「交給小可」環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次要介紹的是小櫻念書的友枝中學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大門設計別緻 門前還有水渠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}教室的天花板很高 有助於學習
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}黑板是彎曲的 便於看清旁邊的字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡是後院 這個拱門超適合說悄悄話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}純白的薔薇飽含了園丁的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:33.20,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你會寫「薔薇」這兩個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能在小櫻落入困境時果斷出手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小鬼在關鍵時刻還能派上點用場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.13,0:24:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次我也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.53,0:24:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世想讓我看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.11,0:24:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這部劇難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.12,0:24:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.30,0:24:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 小櫻的回憶觀賞會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.16,0:24:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
